    Serializable, CriteriaBuilder.Case<T>, Expression<T>, Selection<T>, TupleElement<T>, JpaCriteriaNode, JpaExpression<T>, JpaSearchedCase<T>, JpaSelection<T>, JpaTupleElement<T>, CriteriaNode, ExpressionImplementor<T>, SelectionImplementor<T>, TupleElementImplementor<T>

    public class SearchedCase<T>
extends AbstractExpression<T>
implements JpaSearchedCase<T>
    Models what ANSI SQL terms a searched case expression. This is a CASE expression in the form
     CASE
     WHEN [firstCondition] THEN [firstResult]
     WHEN [secondCondition] THEN [secondResult]
     ELSE [defaultResult]
 END
